title: SMC_NCSymbolResult (Enum)
text:
TYPE SMC_NCSymbolResult :
The possible results of a symbol table lookup.
Attributes:
qualified_only

rows.Name: LOOKING
rows.Comment:
The signature will be retrieved and can be queried
again in the next cycles.

rows.Name: ERROR
rows.Comment:
An error ocurred while looking up the signature, e.g. if the
subprogram could not be found.
